        "YouTube: YouTube Shorts Transcript",
        "YouTube: YouTube Shorts Summarizer",
        "YouTube: YouTube Shorts Stats",
        "YouTube: YouTube Shorts Comments",
        "YouTube: YouTube Channel Shorts",
        "YouTube: YouTube Channel Streams",
        "YouTube: YouTube Hashtag Search",
        "YouTube: YouTube Comment Replies",
        "YouTube: YouTube Channel Playlists",
        "YouTube: YouTube Community Posts",
        "TikTok: TikTok Transcript",
        "TikTok: TikTok Summarizer",
